        {
            "title": "高盛股票交易收入打破華爾街紀錄",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 高盛去年最後三個月股票交易收入突破預期，創下43.1億美元的華爾街史上最高紀錄。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一數字超越了該行2025年第二季度創下的銀行歷史最高紀錄。該行周四在聲明中表示，同時將股息提高至每股4.50美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在執行長David Solomon領導下，高盛優化了交易體系，擴大了投資銀行業務占有率。此前因涉足消費銀行業務失敗而陷入困境，David Solomon重新掌控局面並調整業務重心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在摩根大通、美國銀行、花旗集團和富國銀行本周早些時候公佈財報後，高盛和摩根士丹利成為最後兩家發布第四季度業績的美國大行。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a4d8c172-e0d2-379a-99d3-3c0ef4695bd7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛同時上調了資產與財富管理業務目標，該部門季度手續費收入創紀錄。該公司表示，中期目標是將該部門稅前利潤率從25%左右提升至30%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行2025年淨收入達583億美元，創歷史第二高紀錄。若不計向摩根大通出售Apple Card業務帶來的數十億美元影響，收入本可刷新歷史紀錄。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Goldman Equity Traders Smash Through Wall Street Revenue Record</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E6%89%93%E7%A0%B4%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-125522363.html",
