        {
            "title": "貝萊德資產管理規模升至創紀錄的14萬億美元 ETF大肆吸金",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Company filings\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"1263\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ThxS.apAt_6uomnB4uUHgg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyNjM7Y2Y9d2VicA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7a8f5d60c94947e6fc2775734bb1fd09\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Company filings</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:貝萊德;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/貝萊德\">貝萊德</a>第四財季吸納了3,420億美元的客戶資金，資產管理規模升至創紀錄的14萬億美元。該公司正整合一系列近期收購，加快向私募市場領域擴張。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貝萊德周四在公佈全年及季度業績的聲明中表示，投資者在第四財季向其長期投資基金淨投入2,680億美元，其中有1,810億美元流入ETF業務，使其ETF整體規模達到5.5萬億美元。去年最後三個月的強勁流入推動包括貨幣市場基金和現金管理基金在內的全年總吸金規模達6,980億美元，創下歷史新高。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-85eba0f3-1f11-325b-bdd8-b6aa62414e69-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">長期投資基金的淨流入規模高於彭博調查分析師給出的2,320億美元平均預期。此次業績還首次納入業內規模最大的外包交易之一，花旗委托貝萊德幫助管理約800億美元客戶投資。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「在全球範圍內，客戶正在與貝萊德開展更多合作，」貝萊德執行長Larry Fink在聲明中表示。「我們的業務範圍在產品和地區層面持續拓展，涵蓋公共與私募市場委托、技術與數據，以及客戶渠道。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"1263\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rEb0HeRBgP3F6Wh2.LyuvQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyNjM7Y2Y9d2VicA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9db4e0609781090c92dacea84cb0ebad\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貝萊德第四財季調整後每股純益同比成長10%，至13.16美元。這高於分析師平均預期的12.28美元。營收同比成長23%，至70億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著貝萊德持續加大在私募市場的擴張力度，第四財季運營費用同比大增48%，至53億美元。該公司還將季度現金股息提高10%，至每股5.73美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題BlackRock Total Assets Hit Record $14 Trillion as ETFs Surge (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%9D%E8%90%8A%E5%BE%B7%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E7%9A%8414%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-etf%E5%A4%A7%E8%82%86%E5%90%B8%E9%87%91-133221316.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 22:45:56",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
